quran[32]{c,v,t}:
  1,1,"Ku izina rya Allah, Nyirimpuhwe, Nyirimbabazi"
  1,2,"Ishimwe n’ikuzo byose bikwiye Allah, Nyagasani w’ibiremwa byose"
  1,3,"Nyirimpuhwe, Nyirimbabazi"
  1,4,Umwami w’ikirenga wo ku munsi w’imperuka
  1,5,"Ni wowe (wenyine) dusenga, kandi ni wowe (wenyine) twiyambaza"
  1,6,Tuyobore inzira igororotse
  1,7,"Inzira y’abo wahundagajeho inema, itari iy’abo warakariye cyangwa abayobye"
  2,1,Alif Laam Miim
  2,2,"Icyo ni igitabo (Qur’an) kidashidikanywaho, kikaba umuyoboro ku batinyamana"
  2,3,"Ba bandi bemera ibitagaragara (byahanuwe), bagahozaho iswala (z’itegeko) kandi bagatanga mu byo twabahaye"
  2,4,"Ni na bo bemera ibyo (wowe Muhamadi) wahishuriwe (Qur’an n’imigenzo y’Intumwa), bakanemera ibyahishuwe mbere yawe (ibitabo byahishuriwe Intumwa zakubanjirije), ndetse bakemera imperuka badashidikanya"
  2,5,"Abo ni bo bari mu nzira iboneye yagenwe na Nyagasani wabo, kandi ni bo bakiranutsi"
  2,6,"Mu by’ukuri (wowe Muhamadi), abahakanye wababurira utababurira, byose ni kimwe kuri bo, ntibazemera"
  2,7,"Allah yadanangiye imitima yabo n’ukumva kwabo, ndetse no ku maso yabo (ahashyira) igikingirizo (ibyo byose bituma batemera ukuri), kandi bazahanishwa ibihano bihambaye"
  2,8,No mu bantu hari abavuga bati “Twemeye Allah n’umunsi w’imperuka”; nyamara mu by’ukuri atari abemera
  2,9,"(Bibwira ko) baba babeshya Allah n’abemera, nyamara baba bibeshya ubwabo ariko ntibabyiyumvisha"
  2,10,"Mu mitima yabo harimo uburwayi (bwo gushidikanya n’uburyarya), bityo Allah yarabubongereye; kandi bazahanishwa ibihano bibabaza kubera ko barangwaga no kubeshya"
  2,11,"N’iyo babwiwe bati “Ntimugakore ubwangizi ku isi”, baravuga bati “Ahubwo ni twe dukora ibitunganye.”"
  2,12,"Mu by’ukuri, ni bo bangizi ariko ntibabyiyumvisha"
  2,13,"N’iyo babwiwe bati “Nimwemere nk’uko abandi bantu (abasangirangendo b’Intumwa Muhamadi) bemeye”, baravuga bati “Ese twemere nk’uko abadafite ubwenge bemeye?” Ahubwo ni bo badafite ubwenge ariko ntibabisobanukirwa"
  2,14,"N’iyo bahuye n’abemeye, baravuga bati “Twaremeye.” Nyamara bakwiherera bari kumwe n’ibikomerezwa byabo bibayobora mu buhakanyi, bakavuga bati “Rwose turi kumwe namwe, naho bo (abemeramana) mu by’ukuri tuba tubannyega.”"
  2,15,"Allah arabannyega (aburizamo umugambi wabo), akanabarekera mu kwigomeka kwabo barindagira"
  2,16,"Abo ni bo bahisemo ubuyobe babugurana kuyoboka, ndetse n’amahitamo yabo nta cyo yabunguye; kandi ntibanayobotse"
  2,17,"Urugero rwabo ni nk’urw’ uwacanye umuriro, nuko wamara kumurika no kubonesha ibimukikije byose, Allah agatwara urumuri rwabo, akabasiga mu mwijima batabona"
  2,18,"(Abo bameze) nk’abatumva, abatavuga, ndetse n’abatabona; kandi nta n’ubwo bazisubiraho (ngo bagaruke mu nzira itunganye)"
  2,19,"Cyangwa (urundi rugero rwabo) ni (nk’abantu bagenda) mu mvura nyinshi iva mu kirere, irimo umwijima, inkuba n’imirabyo; bagashyira intoki zabo mu matwi kubera urusaku rwinshi rw’inkuba batinya gupfa. Ariko Allah agose abahakanyi (mu mpande zose)"
  2,20,"Umurabyo uba wenda kubahuma amaso, buri uko ubamurikiye baratambuka, wabazimiraho bagahagarara. Kandi n’iyo Allah aza kubishaka yari kubambura kumva kwabo no kubona kwabo. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Ushobora byose"
  2,21,"Yemwe bantu! Nimusenge Nyagasani wanyu wabaremye, mwe n’abababanjirije; kugira ngo mumugandukire"
  2,22,"We wabagiriye isi nk’isaso (kugira ngo muyigubweho neza) n’ikirere akakigira nk’igisenge, ndetse akanakimanuramo amazi, akayameresha imbuto zikaba amafunguro yanyu. Bityo, ntimukagire izindi mana mubangikanya na Allah, kandi mubizi (ko ari We wenyine ukwiye gusengwa)"
  2,23,"Kandi niba mushidikanya ku byo twahishuriye umugaragu wacu (Muhamadi), ngaho nimuzane igice cya Qur’an (Surat) kimwe kimeze nka yo (Qur’an), ndetse munahamagare abunganizi banyu batari Allah, niba muri abanyakuri"
  2,24,"Niba rero mutabikoze, nta n’ubwo muteze kubikora na mba, ngaho nimwirinde umuriro, wo ibicanwa byawo (bizaba ari) abantu n’amabuye; wateguriwe abahakanyi"
  2,25,"Kandi uhe inkuru nziza ba bandi bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza, ko bazagororerwa ubusitani butembamo imigezi (Ijuru). Buri uko bazajya bafungurirwamo imbuto, bazajya bavuga bati “Izi ni zo twafungurirwaga mbere”, ndetse bazazihabwa zisa (nk’izo baryaga ku isi, ariko zitandukanye mu buryohe). Bazanagororerwamo abafasha basukuye, kandi bazanabubamo ubuziraherezo"